1)FixedThreadPool
Executors.newFixedThreadPool(1);
submit tasks to BlockingQueue
Threads take tasks from Queue, so executed one after another

2) cachedThreadPool
Executors.newCachedThreadPool();
submits task, if no threads are available--> create new thread
If thread is not used within 60 seconds --> kill thread (idle time)

3) scheduledThreadPool
Executors.newScheduledThreadPool(4);

4) singleThread
Executors.newSingleThreadExecutor()
if Thread inside will be killed --> will create new Thread